metadata.name: PLANET #1
metadata.description:
Chimpanzees are not the only cousins humans have. Here is the other part of the story you did not know about.
Around 4 billion years ago, The Meteorite chicxulub was piercing through outer space, carrying the first particles of organic life. It was breaking through the layers of the void with a speed over 20 km per second when it crashed with an asteroidâ€¦
